name: Faces in the dust
description:
"We came here for Salvation".
Whispered the trees to the Earth.
"But you are already saved".
Whispered the Earth in return.
You see the trees had forgotten their connection to the sacred grounds. They had believed they were "just so".
But Earth was the calm reassurer.

"I'm going to show you how much you are needed to enhance and expand the humans consciousness".

Feathers flew and the dust swirled.

Matter is calling home.
Ether is beckoning beyond.

And so this moment was remembered as the time they all witnessed the faces in the dust.
